   "source": [
    "import optimtool as oo\n",
    "from optimtool.base import np, sp, plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "31b22b81-8a97-4d91-84e8-ad120779e16b",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 混合优化算法（optimtool.hybrid）\n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "import optimtool.hybrid as oh\n",
    "oh.[方法名].[函数名]([目标函数], [参数表], [初始迭代点], [正则化参数], [邻近算子名])\n",
    "```\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\phi(x) = f(x) + h(x)\n",
    "$$\n",
    "其中$f(x)$是可微的。$h(x)$不是可微的，并且具备简单的形式。optimtool.hybrid能够选择的$h(x)$有：$||x||_1$, $||x||_2$, $-\\sum_{i}{\\ln(x_i)}$，实例：\n",
    "$$\n",
    "f(x)=\\sum_{i=1}^{n}((n-\\sum_{j=1}^{n}\\cos x_j)+i(1-\\cos x_i)-\\sin x_i)^2, x_0=[0.2, 0.2, ...,0.2]\n",
    "$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "9e51fc70",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import optimtool.hybrid as oh\n",
    "x = sp.symbols(\"x1:3\")\n",
    "f = (2 - (sp.cos(x[0]) + sp.cos(x[1])) + (1 - sp.cos(x[0])) - sp.sin(x[0]))**2 + \\\n",
    "    (2 - (sp.cos(x[0]) + sp.cos(x[1])) + 2 * (1 - sp.cos(x[1])) - sp.sin(x[1]))**2\n",
    "x_0 = (0.2, 0.2) # Random given"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "2314e6c3",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 近似点算法（approt）\n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "oh.approt.[函数名]([目标函数], [参数表], [初始迭代点], [正则化参数], [邻近算子名])\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "| 方法头                                                                                                                                 | 解释                                   |\n",
    "| ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------ |\n",
    "| grad(funcs: FuncArray, args: ArgArray, x_0: PointArray, mu: float=1e-3, proxim: str=\"L1\", tk: float=0.02, verbose: bool=False, draw: bool=True, output_f: bool=False, epsilon: float=1e-4, k: int=0) -> OutputType | 基于梯度方法的邻近近似 |"
   ]
